name: stock_vehicles
title: Stock of road vehicles by municipality, as of 2010
title_en: Stock of road vehicles by municipality, as of 2010
description: This dataset presents the annual stock of road vehicles by municipality, vehicle group (passenger cars, passenger transport vehicles, material transport vehicles, agricultural vehicles, industrial vehicles, motorbikes, trailers) and fuel since 2010.
description_en: This dataset presents the annual stock of road vehicles by municipality, vehicle group (passenger cars, passenger transport vehicles, material transport vehicles, agricultural vehicles, industrial vehicles, motorbikes, trailers) and fuel since of 2010.
